snippet.title: Tiny Dino! Release Trailer (iOS)
snippet.description:
Help your new tiny friend avoid danger in this new cute adventure!
Swipe and spin the planet to help them avoid oncoming doom!
Outrun the fire that rains from the sky across multiple colorful galaxies!
And collect coins to spend on new hats for your dino pal!

● Multiple planets to discover!
● Plenty of hats to collect for your tiny friend!
● Compete with your friends and the world on the Game Center leaderboards!



Available Now on: https://apps.apple.com/us/app/tiny-dino/id1479489808
